1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Want to spot real old money at the airport? Just look at their luggage, how premium it is, how much texture it has, how it stands out.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:19,600
The premium feel is maxed out: full aluminum-magnesium alloy, hand-finished by craftsmen with ten years of experience and over 200 custom rivets. The longer you use it, the better it looks, the little marks and the rivet texture give it real character over time.

3
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:30,300
The accessory colors are all custom, you won't find a second one like it at the airport, and they're really in style right now. Full aluminum-magnesium alloy with rivets, strong and durable, one touch and you'll see why it's worth the price.

4
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:42,700
And no matter how heavy you pack it, even one hundred pounds, it feels like pushing an empty case. A regular suitcase wheel spins five seconds at most, but this one keeps spinning for over a hundred seconds, twenty times smoother.

5
00:00:42,700 --> 00:00:52,000
Even on hotel carpet it rolls effortlessly, the lightest push and it's moving. Once you use it, you'll realize you're not pushing the case, the case is carrying you along.

6
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:04,500
Another plus: compared with a regular case, this one uses an Asymmetrical Split Design, so it holds more at the same size. The deep side fits bulkier items, and this side has a wet and dry separation layer, perfect for both work and travel.

7
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:16,700
It also comes with a TSA combination lock, anti-theft and burst-proof. And best of all, beyond the original accessories, order one set and the shop throws in an extra set of wheels and a handle, free. So, do you like it?
